svn2152:  * Ctrl-C (copy), Ctrl-V (paste), Ctrl-X (cut), Ctrl-Z
	  (undo) and Ctrl-Shift-Z (redo) now work for logs too. The editor
	  doesn't "steal" them anymore. Patch #890.

