	  "Exactly where caret
	  is now" option is chosen (optional validation in case in the
	  middle of a line of code) (bug 1420491)

2006-02-12 15:21  thomasdenk

svn1990:  Patch #823 : Some modifications for compiling under
	  MaxOS X

